><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Ki\u1ec3m k\u00ea \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3: Theo tu\u1ea7n, th\u00e1ng, qu\u00fd \u2013 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c shop c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Ki\u1ec3m k\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9t xu\u1ea5t: Khi nghi ng\u1edd th\u1ea5t tho\u00e1t, sai l\u1ec7ch, ho\u1eb7c sau m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i l\u1edbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; Ki\u1ec3m k\u00ea cu\u1ed1i k\u1ef3: Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft n\u0103m t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><b>1.4 L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi ki\u1ec3m k\u00ea th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m k\u00ea khoa h\u1ecdc mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; T\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a t\u1ed3n kho: tr\u00e1nh d\u01b0 th\u1eeba, gi\u1ea3m chi ph\u00ed l\u01b0u kho<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng: lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 giao \u0111\u00fang h\u1eb9n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch marketing, nh\u1eadp h\u00e0ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8211; T\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 <\/span><b>SuperShip<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/khachhang.supership.vn\/register?referral=S919808\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-6662\" src=\"https:\/\/supership.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/SuperShip-300x100.png\" loading=